# iOS Simulator Preference

## Simulator

Use **iPhone Air** as the default simulator for running tests and builds.

- **Test:** `cd apps/ios && xcodebuild test -scheme portent -configuration Debug -destination 'platform=iOS Simulator,name=iPhone Air,OS=latest'`
- **Build:** `cd apps/ios && xcodebuild build -scheme portent -configuration Debug -sdk iphonesimulator`

When specifying a destination, prefer `name=iPhone Air` over other devices (e.g. iPhone 16, iPhone 17) for consistency across runs.
